Package com.google.gwt.search.client

Core classes used in the AJAX Search API Library for GWT

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
KeepHandler Receives notifications that the user wished to keep a search result.
SearchCompleteHandler Accepts search results.
SearchStartingHandler Accepts search results.
 

Class Summary
BlogResult Blog search results.
BlogSearch A Google blog search.
BookResult Book search results.
BookSearch A Google Book search.
ImageResult Image search results.
ImageSearch A Google Image search.
KeepHandler.KeepEvent A container for arguments of the Keep callback.
LocalResult Local search results.
LocalResult.PhoneNumber A phone number.
LocalSearch A Google local search.
NewsResult A News search result.
NewsResult.Image  
NewsResult.RelatedStory A news story that is related to a primary NewsResult.
NewsSearch A Google News search.
Result The base class from which all search result types derive.
Search A base class for various types of Google searches.
Search.Cursor Tracks the results returned by the search.
Search.Page Represents one page in a search.
SearchCompleteHandler.SearchCompleteEvent A container for arguments of the Search callback.
SearchCompleteHandlerCollection A specialized List that is used to invoke methods on SearchCompleteHandlers.
SearchControl Encapsulates the Google Ajax Search API search control.
SearchControlOptions Used to configure a SearchControl.
SearchStartingHandler.SearchStartingEvent Container for the arguments to a SearchStarting callback.
SearchStartingHandlerCollection A specialized List that is used to invoke methods on SearchStartingHandlers.
SearchUtils Utility methods useful for using the Search API.
VideoResult Video search result.
VideoSearch A Google Video search.
WebResult Web search results.
WebSearch A Google web search query.
 

Enum Summary
AddressLookupMode Used with LocalSearch.setAddressLookupMode(AddressLookupMode).
BookSearchType Used with BookSearch.setSearchType(BookSearchType) to control the types of results displayed.
ColorizationValue Used with ImageSearch.setColorization(ColorizationValue) to control the types of results displayed.
DrawMode Used by SearchControlOptions.setDrawMode(DrawMode).
ExpandMode Determines how results are initially displayed in a SearchControl.
FileTypeValue Used with ImageSearch.setFileType(FileTypeValue) to control the types of results displayed.
ImageSizeValue Used with ImageSearch.setImageSize(ImageSizeValue) to control the types of results displayed.
ImageTypeValue Used with ImageSearch.setImageType(ImageTypeValue) to control the types of results displayed.
KeepLabel Pre-localized labels to use for the "keep" label within a SearchControl.
LinkTarget Sets the target window to display full results in when the user selects a result in a SearchControl.
RestrictType Deprecated. This class is intended for internal library use and is only kept public for backwards compatibility with a few deprecated methods in BookSearch.
RestrictValue Deprecated. see BookSearch.setSearchType(BookSearchType) and BookSearchType
ResultOrder Used with Search objects to determine the manner in which the associated results will be displayed.
ResultSetSize Specifies the desired number of results to retrieve when executing a Search.
SafeSearchValue Used with ImageSearch.setSafeSearch(SafeSearchValue) to control the types of results displayed.
TimeoutInterval Controls the delay between the last keystroke typed into a SearchControl and automatically initiating a search.
